			<div class="bbcode_quote_container"></div>
			
				<div class="bbcode_postedby">
					<img src="images/misc/quote_icon.png" alt="Quote" /> Originally Posted by <strong>Wool</strong>
					<a href="showthread.php?s=030b5bb1eeef6c38cdd5e1505647e8e4&amp;p=1469232#post1469232" rel="nofollow"><img class="inlineimg" src="images/buttons/viewpost-right.png" alt="View Post" /></a>
